link.comment: The component 'lowPassFilter' inside the OpenModelica model 'FilterModels' is semantiqually equivalent to the component 'Front Sensor Filtering' inside the AutoFocus3 model 'ConsistencyTesting' (both are logical elements/components).

The CAD element 'combined_upper_rack' inside the Fusion360 model 'combined_upper_rack' is the 3D geometry of the rack that contains the execution platform, i.e., several Raspberry Pis. It is therefore the physical representation/embodiment of the digital representation of the execution platform inside AF3, called 'Rover Platform'.

The CAD element 'combined_upper_rack' inside the Fusion360 model 'combined_upper_rack' is the 3D geometry of the rack that contains the execution platform, i.e., several Raspberry Pis. It is therefore the physical representation/embodiment of the digital representation of the execution platform inside AF3 which a parameter is stored in the dictionary entry 'PLATFORM_WEIGHT'

The CAD element 'rover' inside the Fusion360 model 'roverAssembly' is the 3D geometry assembly of the rover. It is therefore the physical representation/embodiment of the digital representation of the rover inside AF3 of which a parameter is stored in the dictionary entry 'FRONT_LASER_OFFSET'
